# NOTE: .env and earth-engine-service-account.json ARE baked into the image
# so the ECS task (which has no env_file / volume mount, unlike the Compose
# path) can authenticate with Google Earth Engine and the NVIDIA / data.gov /
# NewsAPI services. Acceptable for this local demo; do not push the image.

